hocles}}, {{an|Mallow}}, {{an|Lillie}}, {{Rotom}}, and {{an|Lana}} narrate the preview for the [[SM128|next episode]].\n* This episode marks the first appearance of a number of Pokémon species in the main series after long absences:\n** {{DL|List of Pokémon with form differences|Shellos and Gastrodon|West Sea}} {{p|Gastrodon}}, who last appeared in \'\'[[DP174|Last Call — First Round!]]\'\', 416 episodes ago.\n** {{DL|List of Pokémon with form differences|Shellos and Gastrodon|East Sea}} Gastrodon, who last appeared in \'\'[[DP186|Familiarity Breeds Strategy!]]\'\', 404 episodes ago.\n** {{p|Mandibuzz}}, who last appeared in \'\'[[BW055|Scraggy and the Demanding Gothita!]]\'\', 354 episodes ago.\n* {{an|Gladion}} reads the [[Who\'s That Pokémon?]] segment in the dub.\n\n===Errors===\n* Gladion is seen [[recall]]ing his {{TP|Gladion|Lycanroc}} into a standard {{i|Poké Ball}}, even though it has previously been shown to be housed in an [[Ultra Ball]].\n\n<gallery>\nSM127 error.png|Lycanroc\'s Poké Ball\n</gallery>\n\n===Dub edits===\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Epilang|color=90BDDC|bordercolor=F1912B\n|zh_cmn={{tt|格拉吉歐與莉莉艾！追尋父親的幻影！！|Gladion and Lillie! Chasing a Father\'s Phantom!!}}\n|ko={{tt|글라디오와 릴리에! 아버지의 환영을 좇아서!!|Gladion and Lillie! Chasing a Father\'s Phantom!!}}\n}}\n{{-}}\n{{EpicodePrevNext|\nprevcode=SM126 |\nprevtitle=Pikachu\'s Exciting Adventure! |\nnextcode=SM128 |\nnexttitle=League Offenders and Defenders! |\nseries=Sun & Moon series |\ncolorscheme=Alola}}\n{{Project Anime notice}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1066}}\n[[Category:Sun & Moon series episodes|127]]\n[[Category:Episodes focusing on Lillie]]\n[[Category:Episodes focusing on Gladion]]\n[[Category:Episodes written by Aya Matsui]]\n[[Category:Episodes storyboarded and directed by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes storyboarded by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes directed by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes animated by Maiko Katsuki]]\n[[Category:Episodes in which a Mythical Pokémon appears]]\n[[Categ